data.title: Most popular artists in Venice on Spotify
data.meta_description: Discover the most popular artists and genres in Venice, Italy on Spotify ranked by the number of listeners.
data.text: This chart is based on The Top 5 cities for each artist on Spotify. Therefore large cities will feature well known international artists, while smaller cities will feature some smaller local artists. The ranking is based on the number of listeners from the city, as provided by Spotify for the top 5 cities for each artist.
